    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the constrained scope of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending and the absence of alternative loading regimes within the standard. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission at Medium assurance level.",
